{
  "info": {
    "name": "Cinema Ticket Booking System",
    "description": "API collection for the Cinema Ticket Booking System.\n\n**การใช้งาน Auth:**\n1. เปิดเบราว์เซอร์ไปที่ http://localhost:8080/auth/google/login แล้ว login ผ่าน Google ให้จบ (จะ redirect ไปที่ frontend พร้อม token ต่อท้าย URL เช่น http://localhost:5173/oauth/callback?token=eyJ...)\n2. คัดลอกค่า token ที่ได้ มาใส่ใน collection variable ชื่อ `token` (คลิกที่ชื่อ Collection > Variables)\n3. ทุก request ที่ต้อง login จะแนบ `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}` ให้อัตโนมัติ\n4. ถ้าอยากทดสอบ endpoint ของ Admin ให้ promote user ให้เป็น admin ก่อนผ่าน mongosh (ดู README หัวข้อ 6) แล้วค่อย login ใหม่/ใช้ token เดิมได้เลย (role เช็คสดจาก DB ไม่ต้อง login ใหม่)\n\nRequest บางตัว (Lock Seats, Create Booking) มี test script ที่ดึงค่า `lock_token` / `booking_id` จาก response มาเก็บใน collection variable ให้อัตโนมัติ เพื่อให้ request ถัดไปในลำดับ (lock → create booking → pay) ใช้ต่อได้เลยโดยไม่ต้อง copy-paste เอง",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8080", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "movie_id", "value": "movie-midnight-in-lumen", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "showtime_id", "value": "movie-midnight-in-lumen-show-2", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "seat_label", "value": "A1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "lock_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "booking_id", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Liveness check",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/health", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["health"] },
            "description": "ตอบ ok เสมอถ้า process ยังรันอยู่ ไม่เช็ค dependency ใดๆ"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Readiness check",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/health/ready", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["health", "ready"] },
            "description": "เช็ค connectivity ไปยัง MongoDB/Redis/Kafka จริง คืน 503 พร้อมระบุตัวที่พัง ถ้ามีอันไหนต่อไม่ได้"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login with Google (open in browser, not Postman)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/google/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["auth", "google", "login"] },
            "description": "เปิด URL นี้ในเบราว์เซอร์จริง ไม่ใช่กดใน Postman เพราะต้อง redirect ไป Google consent screen แล้ว Google จะ redirect กลับมาที่ /auth/google/callback ให้เอง จากนั้น backend จะ redirect ต่อไปที่ frontend พร้อม JWT token ต่อท้าย URL — คัดลอก token นั้นมาใส่ใน collection variable `token`"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get current user (/me)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/me", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "me"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Catalog (public)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List movies",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/movies", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "movies"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get movie by id",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/movies/{{movie_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "movies", "{{movie_id}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List showtimes for movie",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/movies/{{movie_id}}/showtimes", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "movies", "{{movie_id}}", "showtimes"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get showtime by id",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/showtimes/{{showtime_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "showtimes", "{{showtime_id}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get seat map for showtime",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/showtimes/{{showtime_id}}/seats", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "showtimes", "{{showtime_id}}", "seats"] }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Seats (requires login)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Lock seats",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (body.lock_token) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('lock_token', body.lock_token);",
                  "        console.log('Saved lock_token:', body.lock_token);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/showtimes/{{showtime_id}}/seats/lock",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "showtimes", "{{showtime_id}}", "seats", "lock"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"seat_labels\": [\"{{seat_label}}\"]\n}"
            },
            "description": "ล็อกที่นั่งด้วย Redis distributed lock (TTL ตาม LOCK_TTL_SECONDS ค่า default 300 วินาที) response จะมี lock_token เก็บไว้อัตโนมัติผ่าน test script เพื่อใช้ต่อใน Create Booking"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Unlock seats",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/showtimes/{{showtime_id}}/seats/unlock",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "showtimes", "{{showtime_id}}", "seats", "unlock"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"seat_labels\": [\"{{seat_label}}\"],\n  \"lock_token\": \"{{lock_token}}\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "ปลดล็อกที่นั่งก่อนหมดเวลา (ต้องเป็น lock_token เดียวกับที่ล็อกไว้)"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Bookings (requires login)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create booking",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (body.id) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('booking_id', body.id);",
                  "        console.log('Saved booking_id:', body.id);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/bookings", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "bookings"] },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"showtime_id\": \"{{showtime_id}}\",\n  \"seat_labels\": [\"{{seat_label}}\"],\n  \"lock_token\": \"{{lock_token}}\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "ต้องล็อกที่นั่ง (Lock seats) ให้สำเร็จก่อน ถึงจะสร้าง booking ได้ - ใช้ lock_token ที่ได้จาก request ก่อนหน้า"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get booking by id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/bookings/{{booking_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "bookings", "{{booking_id}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Pay booking (success)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/bookings/{{booking_id}}/pay", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "bookings", "{{booking_id}}", "pay"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"result\": \"success\"\n}" }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Pay booking (simulate failure)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/bookings/{{booking_id}}/pay", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "bookings", "{{booking_id}}", "pay"] },
            "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"result\": \"fail\"\n}" }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin (requires ADMIN role)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List all bookings (no filter)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/admin/bookings", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "admin", "bookings"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List bookings (filtered)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/admin/bookings?movie_id={{movie_id}}&date=&user_email=",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "bookings"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "movie_id", "value": "{{movie_id}}" },
                { "key": "date", "value": "", "description": "รูปแบบ YYYY-MM-DD" },
                { "key": "user_email", "value": "", "description": "ค้นหาแบบ substring, case-insensitive" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "ทุก query param เป็น optional และ AND กันได้ (ใส่ค่าไหนว่างไว้ = ไม่ filter ตัวนั้น)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List audit logs",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/admin/audit-logs", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "admin", "audit-logs"] },
            "description": "คืนค่า audit log ล่าสุด 200 รายการ เรียงใหม่สุดก่อน (BOOKING_SUCCESS, BOOKING_TIMEOUT, SEAT_RELEASED, SYSTEM_ERROR)"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "WebSocket (ไม่ใช่ REST - ดูวิธีทดสอบในคำอธิบาย)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Seat map realtime updates",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "ws://localhost:8080/ws/showtimes/{{showtime_id}}?token={{token}}",
              "raw_note": "not a real REST call"
            },
            "description": "นี่ไม่ใช่ REST endpoint แต่เป็น WebSocket - Postman เวอร์ชันใหม่ (v10+) รองรับการสร้าง WebSocket Request แยกได้ (New > WebSocket Request) ให้ paste URL นี้ (แทน localhost:8080 ด้วยที่อยู่จริง และ {{token}} ด้วย JWT จริง) แล้วกด Connect จะเห็น event แบบ {\"type\":\"seat.locked\",\"showtime_id\":\"...\",\"seat_labels\":[...]} ส่งเข้ามาแบบ real-time ทุกครั้งที่มีคนล็อก/ปล่อย/จองที่นั่งสำเร็จในรอบฉายนี้"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
